00:35:12.590 --> 00:35:14.930
FRIEDERIKE FABRITIUS:
To delay gratification?

00:35:14.930 --> 00:35:16.080
AUDIENCE: Yeah,
because that seems what

00:35:16.080 --> 00:35:17.250
you're kind of thesis is there?

