focus on and train one's self,

00:36:00.540 --> 00:36:02.580
and getting in many
sense, a flow, which

00:36:02.580 --> 00:36:03.230
is what you were talking about.

00:36:03.230 --> 00:36:04.855
FRIEDERIKE FABRITIUS:
Yes, in the game,

00:36:04.855 --> 00:36:07.052
but not necessarily
outside the game.

00:36:07.052 --> 00:36:08.760
AUDIENCE: But you can
apply it elsewhere.

00:36:08.760 --> 00:36:09.885
FRIEDERIKE FABRITIUS: Yeah.

00:36:09.885 --> 00:36:13.560
But I think you get more
instant reward in the video game

00:36:13.560 --> 00:36:15.355
than if you do
